    {
      "index": 0,
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "text": "今日はいかがですか？最近の調子は？",
      "file": "000_doctor.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 0,
      "timestamp_end": 5
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "speaker": "patient",
      "text": "...最近、眠れないんです。朝起きるのも辛くて。",
      "file": "001_patient.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 5,
      "timestamp_end": 12
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "text": "何かきっかけはありましたか？",
      "file": "002_doctor.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 12,
      "timestamp_end": 15
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "speaker": "patient",
      "text": "仕事が忙しくて...プレッシャーがすごくて。",
      "file": "003_patient.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 15,
      "timestamp_end": 21
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "text": "食欲はどうですか？",
      "file": "004_doctor.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 21,
      "timestamp_end": 23
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "speaker": "patient",
      "text": "あんまり食べたくないです。体重も3キロ減りました。",
      "file": "005_patient.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 23,
      "timestamp_end": 29
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "text": "気分が落ち込むことは？",
      "file": "006_doctor.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 29,
      "timestamp_end": 32
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "speaker": "patient",
      "text": "はい...何もしたくなくなります。時々、生きてる意味が分からなくて...。",
      "file": "007_patient.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 32,
      "timestamp_end": 42
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "text": "辛いですね。よく話してくれました。",
      "file": "008_doctor.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 42,
      "timestamp_end": 46
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "text": "抗うつ薬を出します。SSRIという種類です。効果が出るまで2〜4週間かかります。",
      "file": "009_doctor.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 46,
      "timestamp_end": 56
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "speaker": "patient",
      "text": "依存性はありますか？",
      "file": "010_patient.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 56,
      "timestamp_end": 58
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "text": "依存性は低いです。でも、急に止めないでください。徐々に減らします。",
      "file": "011_doctor.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 58,
      "timestamp_end": 66
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "text": "睡眠導入剤も出します。短期間だけ使って、睡眠リズムを整えましょう。",
      "file": "012_doctor.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 66,
      "timestamp_end": 74
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "text": "1週間後にまた来てください。もし辛くなったら、いつでも連絡してくださいね。",
      "file": "013_doctor.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 74,
      "timestamp_end": 82
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
